	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64552859">...switch to FOSS apps first. Users can ease themselves into using different apps for their daily needs rather than going all-in at once. Change to one app at a time, e.g. Google Chrome -&gt; Firefox or Chromium, Photoshop -&gt; GIMP, Illustrator -&gt; Inkscape, &amp; MS Office -&gt; LibreOffice, so that you can get used to them before changing OS Windows -&gt; Linux. (And also get used to the idea that you don't have to pay licence fees to use FOSS software!)<br> <br>

Choose the distro with the best support &amp;</div>
	</div>

